Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.52,0:00:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩…佩！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.46,0:00:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.33,0:01:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.19,0:01:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,150)}III、归还之章
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.33,0:01:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.27,0:01:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连你都…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.69,0:01:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.75,0:01:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 抓着我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.43,0:01:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.40,0:02:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.13,0:02:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静下来 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.76,0:02:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就救你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.37,0:02:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓了一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到小姐你就是残存的圣魔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.22,0:02:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜 真是太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.39,0:02:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我也很珍惜自己的生命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.31,0:02:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能就这么放过你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.93,0:02:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红娘 很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.82,0:02:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没空救你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.19,0:02:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和圣魔大人一起死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.34,0:02:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永别了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.87,0:02:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.96,0:02:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣魔殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.37,0:02:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.31,0:02:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.00,0:02:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太迟了 藤井八云
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.55,0:03:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个圣魔小女孩要死在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.70,0:03:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咒鬼 你这家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了 作为无的你也会一起死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.99,0:03:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.38,0:03:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个小女孩的无是藤井…不是真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.14,0:03:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 你是…你是湿婆大人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.75,0:03:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湿婆？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.21,0:03:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么想起来更好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.86,0:03:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.65,0:03:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.91,0:03:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四年前在香港发生的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.37,0:03:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四年前…香港…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.03,0:03:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的…我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.68,0:03:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.36,0:03:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.35,0:03:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.82,0:03:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.61,0:03:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.72,0:04:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.37,0:04:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫 好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.67,0:04:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.56,0:04:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.28,0:04:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为这样就结束了 藤井
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.39,0:04:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.55,0:04:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你们悲惨命运的开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.72,0:04:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣魔小女孩哟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.27,0:04:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点想起真正的你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.58,0:04:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后诅咒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.14,0:04:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法逃避的真实的你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.37,0:04:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.16,0:05:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小女孩是湿婆大人封印的帕尔提…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.39,0:05:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…圣堂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.10,0:05:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.57,0:05:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云先生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.48,0:05:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…你是湿婆大人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.73,0:05:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湿婆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.76,0:05:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起来吧 真正的你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.10,0:06:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.28,0:06:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是无吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.39,0:06:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法以自己的意志寻求死亡的可悲生物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.91,0:06:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个小女孩是三只眼的后裔 而你是无？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.61,0:06:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的生命在佩体内
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要佩不死 我的身体就会无限次复原
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.89,0:06:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.22,0:06:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说你是保护那小女孩的骑士了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.98,0:06:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.85,0:06:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明不明白 不老不死不是人类该有的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.01,0:06:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为生命有限才显得宝贵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.58,0:06:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不老不死这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都半信半疑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然真的有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诱拐了三只眼的小女孩 我就能成为亿万富翁了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.77,0:06:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的人！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.01,0:06:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.51,0:06:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向着青春Let's go吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.81,0:07:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真羡慕你啊 这么有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.72,0:07:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.05,0:07:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.42,0:07:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨…笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差点射到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.55,0:07:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这孩子的错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只是被人操控了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.76,0:07:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.71,0:07:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说不定什么时候还会攻击我们 是敌人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是那样也不能轻易夺走他人珍贵的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.84,0:07:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能那么做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.23,0:07:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.08,0:07:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.09,0:07:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是个可悲的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.36,0:07:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.18,0:07:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.64,0:07:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.11,0:07:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.86,0:07:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.81,0:07:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如佩所说的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:08:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有夺走别人生命的权利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.46,0:08:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你放过她吧 麦当劳先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.88,0:08:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.90,0:08:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.02,0:08:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 麦当劳先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.27,0:08:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.40,0:08:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣魔大人的请求怎么能推辞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你男朋友都吃醋了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.01,0:08:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.38,0:08:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 什么男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.08,0:08:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦当劳先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.63,0:08:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不也有很好的方面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被那位大人迷住了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.60,0:08:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.08,0:08:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点去圣地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.08,0:08:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝物在等着我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你不是想要找回喜欢的女孩的记忆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.04,0:08:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.10,0:08:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.81,0:08:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦当劳先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我到这里就要跟大家分别了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为保护圣堂的人 不能再深入了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.00,0:09:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢这段时间的照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳巴鲁巴先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿圣光保佑圣魔大人顺利到达圣地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.31,0:09:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僧院长大人的灵魂也能安息了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要把不老不死之术拿到手才回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.57,0:09:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待我的表现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.97,0:09:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一点都不期待
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.17,0:09:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女士们先生们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.86,0:09:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为我们中间唯一的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.71,0:09:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将用血来打开通往圣地的路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.74,0:09:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要感谢我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.08,0:09:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请保重
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:10:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠 小玲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.74,0:11:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在东京过得如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.15,0:11:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校没什么变化吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在新学期已经开始了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.02,0:11:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于来到了我的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.97,0:11:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.41,0:11:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能恢复吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.53,0:11:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢复后我会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.50,0:11:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠 小玲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.22,0:11:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成…成功了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.47,0:11:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是做梦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:11:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:11:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.28,0:11:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.46,0:12:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.17,0:12:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我就能成为亿万富翁了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.48,0:12:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.09,0:12:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.82,0:12:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.95,0:12:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不会真的跟传闻一样已经全灭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生什么事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣魔呢 圣魔小女孩们在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.86,0:12:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.25,0:12:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些排列在这里的东西是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.28,0:12:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.56,0:12:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.52,0:12:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…坟墓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.67,0:12:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些全部是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.23,0:12:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟传闻一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.98,0:13:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是鬼眼王和三只眼一族最后的斗争吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.61,0:13:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是悲哀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.36,0:13:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有着不老不死的力量 但是在战争面前还是无能为力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能改变任何事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.65,0:14:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几百年前被记录在这魔法阵中的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.65,0:14:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩年幼时的口信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.90,0:14:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概只会对三只眼产生反应吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到这里 旅行中的同胞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.53,0:14:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是帕尔提四世
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.38,0:14:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出生于天空中白龙飞舞之年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.08,0:14:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是最后的三只眼吽迦罗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.51,0:14:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.89,0:14:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该对从远方到圣地来的你们表示欢迎的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.60,0:14:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在还是请回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.41,0:14:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 请不要再次踏入此地了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同富饶的大地一同诞生的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.28,0:15:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三只眼吽迦罗悠久的历史已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.39,0:15:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我未来的丈夫湿婆一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.93,0:15:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.77,0:15:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他本来是很温柔的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.96,0:15:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道为什么变成了可怕的恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.64,0:15:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当他那族里最强大的力量觉醒的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.11,0:15:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的不幸就开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.14,0:15:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量就是一切
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是他的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.14,0:15:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了 我们一族都厌恶那种暴力行为
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.94,0:15:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我们想向他表示反对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.17,0:15:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们做错了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们选择了用力量对抗他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.03,0:16:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然把湿婆 也就是鬼眼王成功封印于圣魔石
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.01,0:16:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是全族除了我之外全部未能幸免
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.94,0:16:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要离开这个不祥之地了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后舍弃力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.74,0:16:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为人类
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.66,0:16:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为能牺牲自我 保护他人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.15,0:16:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有神圣之力的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.47,0:16:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神圣…之力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也请你们忘记这个地方的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.04,0:16:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不要把鬼眼王唤醒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.94,0:16:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.63,0:17:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是令人伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.43,0:17:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼眼王是湿婆 佩是帕尔提
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.46,0:17:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是湿婆的未婚妻…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湿婆？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.43,0:17:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,印度神话中的破坏神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当这个世界堕落的时候就把一切摧毁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让宇宙回到混沌的神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.14,0:17:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.00,0:17:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真没想过会跟传说中的神这么有缘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.95,0:17:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我头脑都有点混乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.62,0:17:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个不好的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.98,0:17:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之要先找出恢复你记忆的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.53,0:17:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还真奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.28,0:17:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来以为来圣地的话 那些家伙肯定会出现的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.66,0:17:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么气息呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.32,0:17:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.24,0:17:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非要恢复记忆不可吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.33,0:17:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.55,0:18:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.02,0:18:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.88,0:18:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是帕尔提
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.36,0:18:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时又是鬼眼王的未婚妻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.60,0:18:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有我体内还有另外一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.46,0:18:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不怎么相信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.15,0:18:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但全是真的对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.46,0:18:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将来会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再有悲伤的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.40,0:18:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云先生不是也说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.67,0:18:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些事还是不知道更好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.16,0:18:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.62,0:18:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.17,0:18:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气死人了 什么鬼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.05,0:18:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么值钱的都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.82,0:18:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是什么圣地 简直是胡扯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.49,0:19:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛这么哭丧着脸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.46,0:19:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.01,0:19:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩第一次出现在我面前时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.90,0:19:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说过想成为人类
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想得太简单了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.40,0:19:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为三只眼吽迦罗一族的她 一出生便背负这种命运
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.10,0:19:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起长年悲惨地一个人生存
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.10,0:19:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩希望成为人类 过着无忧无虑 随意哭笑的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.54,0:19:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和死党们一起玩乐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.45,0:19:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真惭愧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.14,0:19:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她心中隐藏着如此伟大的志向
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.78,0:19:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说想成为人类其实是自我的牺牲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护所爱的世界的力量就在人类手中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.55,0:19:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.20,0:19:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.22,0:19:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类有那种力量吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.95,0:19:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在自言自语什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.77,0:20:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不是听到圣魔殿下是鬼眼王的未婚妻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.96,0:20:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就心凉了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.96,0:20:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.54,0:20:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心 你至少也有那么一点「神圣」之力的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.75,0:20:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是因为我是不死之身
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.58,0:20:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.84,0:20:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不是「无」大概也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.58,0:20:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为所爱的人不顾一切地牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.42,0:20:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只有人类对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.56,0:20:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到自己的最爱并不顾一切地保护
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许就是所谓的神圣之力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦当劳先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.27,0:20:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正不要做会让自己后悔的事就是了 对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.53,0:21:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也真对不起八云先生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.72,0:21:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我自己说不后悔来到这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.97,0:21:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.37,0:21:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很想回东京
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 恢复记忆什么的都不需要了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.27,0:21:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦的记忆恢复了也没什么用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.59,0:21:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是绫小路佩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.67,0:21:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么看都是个普通女高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.31,0:21:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且现在已经遇到了喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.40,0:21:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要像现在这样就好 像现在这样喜欢着八云先生就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.81,0:21:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后大家一起住在东京
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.52,0:21:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我最喜欢的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.59,0:21:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样决定好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.12,0:21:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我体内陌生的另一个我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.92,0:21:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.39,0:21:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.62,0:22:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.72,0:22:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是圣者的归来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.96,0:22:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是辛苦你了 化蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.52,0:22:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来抑制着三只眼的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.56,0:22:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值得表扬 化蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.66,0:22:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.04,0:22:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是绫小路佩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.62,0:22:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕尔提四世
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.94,0:22:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到连你自己都失去记忆了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.71,0:22:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.20,0:22:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的仆人化蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.83,0:22:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.11,0:23:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云先生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.72,0:23:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我 八云…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.95,0:23:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.51,0:23:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.53,0:23:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像听到什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.58,0:23:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都没听到啊 没什么异常
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.88,0:23:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咒鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.28,0:23:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们就去当鬼眼王大人复活的祭品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.11,0:23:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼眼王…复活…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.19,0:23:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.72,0:23:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.87,0:23:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦当劳先生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.20,0:24:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以藤井八云之名下令！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.83,0:24:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来吧 土爪！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.77,0:24:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班门弄斧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.41,0:24:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你见识下我们魔道最大的奥义吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.27,0:24:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.50,0:25:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也长眠于我肚子里的亚空间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.42,0:25:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这头怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.84,0:25:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还能跑吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.50,0:25:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勉强可以
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.98,0:25:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.04,0:25:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.38,0:25:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.96,0:25:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.96,0:25:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.42,0:25:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你们吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.92,0:25:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.80,0:26:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知死活的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.57,0:26:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我 八云先生
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.36,0:26:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.79,0:26:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云先生
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.86,0:26:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云先生
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.63,0:26:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃吧 化蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.95,0:26:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用心灵感应向「无」求救也是白费力气
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.02,0:26:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人会来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.93,0:26:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是谁都无法救你
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.83,0:27:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,废物
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.49,0:27:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 化蛇！觉醒吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.28,0:27:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.31,0:27:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起来吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.61,0:27:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四年前的那天 在香港发生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.49,0:27:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会有人妨碍你了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.25,0:27:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉醒吧 化蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.46,0:27:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真实的姿态 记起来吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.44,0:27:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四年前的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.93,0:27:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在香港发生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.94,0:27:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.81,0:27:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香港？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.49,0:27:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底是
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.43,0:28:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 贝纳雷斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.73,0:28:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.79,0:28:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到找到了三只眼吽迦罗的幸存者
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.78,0:28:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么处置她？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.65,0:28:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三只眼的幸存者
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.76,0:28:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是稍微吓吓她
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.31,0:28:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就快到这里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.27,0:28:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不就妨碍鬼眼王大人的复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.89,0:28:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想杀了她
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.88,0:28:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是很难得的三只眼 想直到鬼眼王复活都让她活着
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.20,0:28:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后 把她的活力注入刚复活很虚弱的王的身体里
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.38,0:28:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.08,0:28:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用穿灵菱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.74,0:28:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.46,0:28:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来吧 化蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.51,0:28:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化蛇？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.48,0:29:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这任务交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.36,0:29:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要封印三只眼的记忆 化蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.59,0:29:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…蛇？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.07,0:29:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是化蛇？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.52,0:29:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起来吧 化蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.64,0:29:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时的情形
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.57,0:29:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.91,0:30:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.91,0:30:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的记忆丢失了 在香港的大街上徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.39,0:30:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.95,0:30:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和奶奶收养
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.88,0:30:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.28,0:30:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白了？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.18,0:30:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你既不是帕尔提也不是绫小路佩
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.08,0:30:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的真身变为额头上封印
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.51,0:30:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抑制三只眼吽迦罗的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.20,0:30:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你进入了那身体里 你就是我的仆人化蛇！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.12,0:30:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然穿灵菱能转移不同人的人格
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.08,0:30:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是对于拥有双重人格的三只眼而言 并不完全
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.04,0:30:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然封住了「佩」的意识
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.01,0:30:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也使三只眼失去了记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.26,0:30:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但化蛇你也被影响了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.24,0:30:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记了自我
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.25,0:31:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了取回记忆 消灭我们而到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.25,0:31:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在的你别说我了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.56,0:31:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连封印在此的王也不可能被你打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.40,0:31:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼眼王在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.68,0:31:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在只有两条路
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.77,0:31:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一是服从我们 以人类的姿态回到原来的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.01,0:31:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二是让三只眼苏醒 杀死我和鬼眼王
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.01,0:31:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴着你手上的湿婆之爪 念出「鲁德拉 姆瑟迪」的话
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.78,0:31:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一来 「三只眼」和「佩」都会苏醒
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.29,0:31:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过让佩苏醒的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.84,0:31:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也会恢复成丑陋的化蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.99,0:31:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是化蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.37,0:31:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是化蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.91,0:32:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.14,0:32:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.12,0:32:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦当劳先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.52,0:32:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝纳雷斯
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.17,0:32:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见 少年
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.25,0:32:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 你敢动佩一根毫毛 就让你好看
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.14,0:32:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我住口 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.10,0:32:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.95,0:32:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.89,0:32:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.55,0:32:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来把头捏碎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.02,0:32:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真难看啊 少年
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.71,0:32:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.32,0:32:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不住手的话 我就杀了鬼眼王
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.63,0:32:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.34,0:32:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.07,0:32:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你住手
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.28,0:33:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并没有奢望什么
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.26,0:33:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣地的事 鬼眼王的事
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.98,0:33:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想全部都忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.70,0:33:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以让我们平安回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.86,0:33:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊 佩
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.82,0:33:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印被解开的话 我们回去有什么意义啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.92,0:33:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.46,0:33:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以放弃啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.24,0:33:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.96,0:33:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样没有过去记忆地活着
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.26,0:33:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有什么不好吧？八云先生
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.15,0:33:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 那僧院长岂不是白死了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.60,0:33:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能哭啊 佩
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.44,0:33:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能轻易地退缩
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.25,0:33:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相总是很残酷的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.20,0:33:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要振作 拿出自信 不要退缩
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.08,0:33:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僧院长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.18,0:34:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.58,0:34:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.64,0:34:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不敢了？化蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.78,0:34:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能做到的话就做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.71,0:34:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 你想怎么做？化蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.62,0:34:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是你的仆人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.29,0:34:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是绫小路佩
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.80,0:34:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Baras
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.23,0:34:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vidahi
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.63,0:34:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.07,0:34:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.76,0:34:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该跟你说过
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.55,0:34:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的你没有胜算
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.07,0:34:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僧院长
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.33,0:35:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们将会死在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.58,0:35:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会饶恕你们
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.45,0:35:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 你要怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.39,0:35:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只有两条路可以选择
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.56,0:35:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僧院长
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.22,0:35:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把力量赐予我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.89,0:35:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化蛇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.53,0:35:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.55,0:35:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僧院长
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.06,0:35:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.27,0:35:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.72,0:35:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.34,0:35:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.75,0:35:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.89,0:35:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.28,0:36:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.77,0:36:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像连我也沾了不死之身的光
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.90,0:36:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云先生
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.57,0:36:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.98,0:36:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去救出你的公主吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.24,0:36:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总要有个结尾
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.15,0:36:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不死的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.33,0:36:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云先生
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.10,0:36:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思我明白了 化蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.40,0:36:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.98,0:36:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.52,0:36:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要杀了你们所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.75,0:36:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.81,0:37:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.55,0:37:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.79,0:37:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.20,0:37:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镜蛊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.41,0:37:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消灭他了？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.53,0:37:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.26,0:37:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的力量是伤不了我的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.52,0:37:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩 你快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.88,0:38:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能服从于他
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.57,0:38:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我被封印 只有你孤独一人
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.22,0:38:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要消灭鬼眼王
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.60,0:38:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云先生
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.61,0:38:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.81,0:38:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何都要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.05,0:38:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起变成人类
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.35,0:38:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成人类
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.13,0:38:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的生命与你同在 不论何时都在你心中
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.01,0:38:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.35,0:38:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想失去
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.70,0:38:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.18,0:38:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.57,0:38:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.49,0:39:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.60,0:39:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.49,0:39:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云先生
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.01,0:39:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.67,0:39:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活下去！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.90,0:39:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.54,0:39:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要去
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.80,0:40:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云先生
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.04,0:40:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.90,0:40:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后面就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.70,0:40:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去跟你的骑士快乐生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.34,0:40:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.96,0:40:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦当劳先生
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.22,0:40:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.72,0:40:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.33,0:40:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.84,0:40:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.57,0:40:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.96,0:40:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.61,0:40:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云先生！八云先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.75,0:40:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在再问一次 是服从我来救他们
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.39,0:41:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是让三只眼苏醒 消灭我和鬼眼王？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.34,0:41:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你能在他面前变回丑陋的原形吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.74,0:41:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.39,0:41:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.21,0:41:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃啊 佩！
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.29,0:41:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你决定了是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.27,0:41:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以啊 佩
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.63,0:41:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四年前
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.18,0:41:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我醒来时 身旁有爷爷和奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.65,0:41:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我感到非常地幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.49,0:41:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我说什么都想不起来时
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.50,0:41:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就对我说「可怜的孩子」
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.47,0:41:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的对我非常地爱护
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.68,0:41:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.06,0:41:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠和小玲是在我中学时认识的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.23,0:41:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.02,0:41:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使不去什么特别的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.36,0:42:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要三个人在一起 我就觉得很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.84,0:42:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放学后一起说笑 不断地聊着天
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.70,0:42:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原以为这样的时光会持续到永远…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.43,0:42:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我所拥有的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.71,0:42:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪亮的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.75,0:42:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 八云先生
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.01,0:42:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然过着幸福快乐的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.91,0:42:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却总觉得少了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.15,0:42:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云先生和大家告诉了我答案
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.39,0:42:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一定就是「神圣之力」
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.42,0:42:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.42,0:42:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很感谢你 八云先生
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.46,0:43:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永别了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.52,0:43:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.77,0:43:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会听从于你
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.04,0:43:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁德拉
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.96,0:43:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姆瑟迪
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.86,0:44:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何你都要去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.27,0:45:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣地的废墟堆积如山
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.72,0:45:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能查出鬼眼王的生死吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.63,0:45:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受穿灵菱影响 佩现在还没苏醒
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.67,0:45:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没苏醒？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.86,0:45:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她醒来前 我想到圣地静养一下
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.38,0:45:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.54,0:45:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过佩不是只丧失了记忆吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.70,0:45:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那并非吾
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.52,0:45:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是凭依在吾身上的化蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.23,0:45:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.20,0:45:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.08,0:45:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么那家伙 绫小路怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.73,0:45:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不是吾很失望吗？八云
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.32,0:45:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 她没死
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.98,0:45:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过改变了容貌而已
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.48,0:46:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾马上就回来
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.77,0:46:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在东京等吾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.87,0:46:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东京？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.38,0:46:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佩
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.45,0:46:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佩
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.70,0:46:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.09,0:46:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.47,0:46:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.33,0:46:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为你不会再醒过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.90,0:47:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们好担心
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.87,0:47:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是变成蛇了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.33,0:47:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.81,0:47:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.00,0:47:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得很怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.09,0:47:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.03,0:47:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总觉得做了一场很长的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.80,0:47:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.89,0:47:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保重了 化蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.39,0:47:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云先生
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.31,0:47:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.95,0:47:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云这个名字不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.34,0:47:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.69,0:48:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我心花怒放
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.13,0:48:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.65,0:48:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很棒的男朋友吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.23,0:48:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如在可以眺望港口的公园里
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.24,0:48:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和喜欢的他一起倾听遥远的汽笛声
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.03,0:48:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在夜晚的星空下对我告白
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.42,0:48:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.74,0:48:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌


